points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1ada')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1ada" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>never give in except to convictions of honour and <strong>good sense</strong>. <em>Never yield to force</em>; never yield to the <em>apparently overwhelming might of the enemy</em>.</p>
